9-11 Babel Road features a well-located corner site of 5,210sqm* improved with 1,054sqm of functional medical centre improvements.  The property is strategically located just 400 metres* from the Welshpool road/Leach Highway intersection being just 10km* from the Perth CBD and 8km* from the Perth international airport terminal.  

The property is available for lease and for sale with vacant possession providing an opportunity for tenants, owner occupiers and developers.  The owner will consider refurbishing the existing improvements subject to lease terms.

KEY FEATURES:
•Medical Improvements of 1,054 sqm* comprising:
o	Medical & Administration – 702 sqm*
o	Physiotherapy rooms – 257sqm*
o	Boardroom/offices – 95sqm*
o      Hydrotherapy pool
•Land Area: 5,210sqm*
•Proximity to Leach Highway and Welshpool Road
•60 Parking Bays* 
•Combined Street Frontage of 117sqm* 
•Dual Street Access
•Zoned “General Industrial” providing for a range of uses and redevelopment options
•Vacant possession at settlement 
•10km* from Perth CBD
•8km* from Perth International Airport

For further information or to book a viewing of this diverse medical/industrial facility, please contact the exclusive sales agents.

CBRE is pleased to present for sub lease 269B Treasure Road, Welshpool. The subject building represents an "A" Grade Office/Workshop/Warehouse facility

OFFICE Concrete footings and floors, concrete tilt up walls with aluminium glazed elevations, suspended panel ceiling, fluorescent lighting, new carpets and refrigerated air conditioning.

WORKSHOP/WAREHOUSE Concrete footings and floors and wall panels, Steel portal frame and a metal clad roof. Includes runway beams with an under beam height of 6.1 metres and an under truss height of between 7.57 and 8 metres. The roof is insulated and includes new skylights and high bay lighting. The ablutions are built within the workshop at the rear
of the offices.

Access is via one front and two side roller shutter doors that are 4.7 metres wide and 5.2 metres high. There are 15.5 marked car bays for the use of the subject building.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: As New "A" Grade office/workshop with side laydown

Quality warehousing facilty !!!!

Located in Welshpool, one of Perth’s premier commercial and industrial districts and situated nearby Perth’s International and Domestic Airports, major highways including Leach Highway, Tonkin Highway and the newly extended Roe Highway.

118 Dowd Street has a total site area of 12,800sqm* and comprises an office and workshop facility totaling 3,086sqm*.

The main office and amenities area which has been extended and extensively refurbished has an area of 412sqm* with the existing, refurbished workshop having an area of 2,674sqm* with the ability to be extended by a further 1,500sqm*. The
balance of the site comprises a combination of concrete, asphalt and road base hardstand areas, a newly created second crossover onto Dowd Street allowing for full drive around access, reconfigured staff and customer parking and new
landscaping.
